\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Another group of farmers is also not knowledgeable about the true relationship
 between 
\begin_inset Formula $Y_{it}^{H}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{it}$
\end_inset

.
 But unlike Type 3 and 4 farmers, they underestimate the adoption premium
