\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citet
key "doi:10.1086/703868"
literal "false"

\end_inset

), perhaps due to a disappointing experience in the past.
 Some of these farmers, Type 5 in Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "types of farmers"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

, adopt at baseline as the expected marginal return may still be larger
