 For another fraction of farmers that underestimate the adoption premium,
 referred to as Type 6 in Table 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "types of farmers"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

, the expected marginal return will be less than the marginal cost of adoption,
